Knight Grand Cross of the Royal Victorian Order (United Kingdom)
Knight Grand Cross of the Order of the Tower and Sword (Portugal)
Knight Grand Cross of the Order of St. Olav (Norway)
Knight of the Order of St. Andrew (Russia)
Knight Grand Cross of the Order of St. Stanislaus
Knight Grand Cross of the Order of Saint Alexander Nevsky
